        <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/repaying-your-student-loan/what-you-pay" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Student loan repayment rates — GOV.UK</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        For a complete overview of all tax rates this year, see our <a href="/guides/uk-tax-year-2026-27/">UK Tax Year 2026/27 guide</a>.
      </p>

    </article>
  </Fragment>
</CalculatorLayout>
